  "implementationNotes": [
    "This pass treats prior T17-T26 talent cleanup phases as applied and focuses on remaining Jedi/lightsaber/Mystic/Telepath/Sith adjacent leftovers.",
    "Unsafe embedded Active Effects were removed from scoped talents and replaced with action/reference cards or explicitly safe metadata.",
    "Force Persuasion no longer depends on embedded Active Effects: the derived skill calculator now treats Persuasion as trained and substitutes Use the Force when better, matching the existing Force Deception/Force Treatment pattern.",
    "Vaapad, Sentinel Strike, Reap Retribution, Master of the Great Hunt, and Dark Scourge gained opt-in/contextual attack-option metadata where the existing resolver can support it.",
    "Several reactions are now registered in owned talent metadata for the reaction-engine surface, but some require future post-hit/post-threshold event windows before they can auto-surface every time."
  ],
  "remainingLimitations": [
    "Psychic Citadel is now a clean reference card instead of an unsafe Active Effect, but its class-level Will Defense formula still needs a class-specific-level resolver before it should become automatic.",
    "Ataru and Master of Elegance require true damage ability substitution, not additive Dexterity damage; they remain reference cards until the damage formula can replace Strength cleanly.",
    "Niman, Jar Kai, Makashi, Shii-Cho, Soresu, and Shoto Pin Block interact with Block/Deflect/Lightsaber Defense state and remain action/reference cards pending deeper Block/Deflect state mutation support.",
    "Djem So, Defensive Roll, Visionary Attack, and Visionary Defense have reaction metadata, but require post-hit/post-miss/post-threshold event bridges to surface automatically."
  ],
